Investors may be:


* [[Consumer]]s pre-paying for some product but receiving co-ownership in the [[Physical Sources]].  For example, a group of consumers could buy a milk dairy so they can receive the milk [[At Cost]] and under their full control.

* [[Worker]]s committing to perform some amount of labor or achieve some amount of results within some frame of time.  In a better world this [[Promise to Pay]] can be used as a personally issued currency.

* Angels who inject resources ([[Money]] or [[Capital]]) with the plan to extract [[Price Above Cost]] from consumers who do not yet have sufficient property ownership in [[Physical Sources]].